                    <x-admin-core::card>
                        <x-slot:header>The sidebar, routes &amp; access — wired for you</x-slot>
                        <p>You never add the menu by hand. One <code>admin-core:make</code> wires the whole screen:
                            migration, model, controller, form requests, views, an optional JSON API
                            (<code>--api</code>), a <strong>sidebar link</strong>, and a permission set
                            (<code>list-</code>, <code>create-</code>, <code>update-</code>,
                            <code>delete-{resource}</code>) — all granted to the
                            <x-admin-core::badge tone="secondary">admin</x-admin-core::badge> super-role, so it works
