                            <ol class="mb-0 mt-1">
                                <li><strong>Caches</strong> — run
                                    <code>php artisan config:clear route:clear view:clear</code>. The menu lives in
                                    <code>config/admin-core.php</code>; a cached config (or compiled views) keeps the
                                    old sidebar.</li>
                                <li><strong>Permissions</strong> — the sidebar <em>hides links you can't open</em>.
                                    Sign in as <code>admin@example.com</code>, or grant your role the
                                    <code>list-{resource}</code> permission under <strong>Access &rsaquo; Roles</strong>.</li>
                                <li><strong>Migrate</strong> — run <code>php artisan migrate</code> so the screen's
